title: Episode 64: Ft Cyn Santana & Betty Idol
itunes:title: Episode 64: Ft Cyn Santana & Betty Idol
description:
Cyn Santana and Betty Idol unite from Love and Hip Hop New York and Atlanta as guests on Lip Service and play a game of Lip Service Family Feud. They discuss the top 5 ways you can tell a man is whupped, how you can tell a man is undercover, and the top 5 positions in the bedroom. They give their tip of the day with Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago and Gigi Maguire about recovering from leaked nudes and/or sex tapes. Do you own it or ignore it?
